        <h2 class="fw-bold  w-100 text-center sub-header">Minimalist Designs: Why Less is More</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <p class="w-100 lead">Have you ever scrolled past an ad so cluttered with details that you didn’t even know where to look? That’s the exact problem minimalist designs aim to solve in advertising design. In a world overflowing with noise, less truly is more. By stripping designs down to their essentials, you can grab attention and leave a lasting impression without overwhelming your audience.</p>
