      <div class="col">
        <p class="w-100 lead">Video ads are everywhere these days, and it’s not hard to see why—they grab attention, tell a story, and stick in your memory. But if you’re a startup or small business with a tight budget, creating video ads might feel out of reach. Don’t worry! With the right approach, you can craft compelling video ads without breaking the bank. Let’s dive into some best practices to make your advertising design shine, even on a shoestring budget.</p>
