    <h3 class="fw-bold text-secondary mt-4">Why Video Ads Are Worth It</h3>
    <p class="w-100 lead">Video ads are no longer a luxury reserved for big brands. Thanks to advances in technology and free tools, startups and small businesses can create engaging ads without overspending. By focusing on storytelling, simplicity, and smart advertising design, you can connect with your audience and grow your brand—no blockbuster budget required.<br/><br/>
      So grab your phone, get creative, and start experimenting with video ads today. Who knows? Your next 15-second masterpiece could be the ad that puts your business on the map.      
      
      </p>
