      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <p class="w-100 lead">When it comes to advertising design, the colors you choose can make or break your campaign. Bright and bold tones shout “Look at me!” while subtle and soft hues whisper sophistication and calm. But which one is right for your brand? The answer lies in understanding your niche, your audience, and the emotions you want to evoke. Let’s explore how to make the perfect color choice for your advertising design.</p>
